OL,3,CTeachers on strike over 'abusive pupil
OL,4,Cbehaviour threatening safety' of staff
OL,6,FA group of teachers in Gloucestershire
OL,7,Fare on strike over what they say has
OL,8,Fbeen a failure of school management to
OL,9,Faddress abusive pupil behaviour.
OL,11,FMembers of NASUWT - The Teachers'
OL,12,FUnion at Tewkesbury Academy took the
OL,13,Ffirst of five planned days of strike
OL,14,Faction on Wednesday 4 February, after
OL,15,Fbeing subjected to threats of
OL,16,Fviolence, derogatory language and
OL,17,Fverbal abuse from a minority of
OL,18,Fstudents.
