OL,3,CTeachers on strike over 'abusive pupil
OL,4,Cbehaviour threatening safety' of staff
OL,6,FThese teachers have accused their
OL,7,Femployer of failing to address their
OL,8,Fconcerns, but Tewkesbury Academy says
OL,9,Fit implements approaches designed to
OL,10,Fimprove standards for all children.
OL,12,FMeanwhile, the NASUWT teachers say
OL,13,Fthat unacceptable student behaviour is
OL,14,Faffecting not only their ability to
OL,15,Fteach, but threatening the health and
OL,16,Fsafety of both staff and pupils.
OL,18,FAccording to them, these disruptive
OL,19,Fpupils also frequently interrupt
OL,20,Flessons that they are not part of.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
