OL,3,CTeachers on strike over 'abusive pupil
OL,4,Cbehaviour threatening safety' of staff
OL,6,FIn 2023, a teenager who stabbed a
OL,7,Fmaths teacher at the school was sent
OL,8,Fto youth detention for 14 months.
OL,10,FMatt Wrack, NASUWT General Secretary,
OL,11,Fsaid: "Rather than fulfilling their
OL,12,Fresponsibilities to ensure an orderly,
OL,13,Fsafe and focused teaching and learning
OL,14,Fenvironment for staff and pupils at
OL,15,FTewkesbury Academy, management have
OL,16,Finstead chosen to seek to intimidate
OL,17,Fstaff who have raised concerns about
OL,18,Fpupil behaviour.
OL,26,@sD@GOU
