OL,3,CTeachers on strike over 'abusive pupil
OL,4,Cbehaviour threatening safety' of staff
OL,6,F"We have exhausted every avenue to
OL,7,Fresolve this dispute, but the lack of
OL,8,Faction to keep staff and pupils safe
OL,9,Ffrom abuse and disruptive behaviour
OL,10,Ffrom a small number of students has
OL,11,Fleft us with no other choice but to
OL,12,Ftake strike action.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
