OL,3,CTeachers on strike over 'abusive pupil
OL,4,Cbehaviour threatening safety' of staff
OL,6,F"We have given management numerous
OL,7,Fopportunities to work with us to put
OL,8,Fin place an effective pupil behaviour
OL,9,Fmanagement system, but they have
OL,10,Ffailed to do so.
OL,12,F"No school can operate effectively
OL,13,Fwithout a robust behaviour management
OL,14,Fsystem, which is consistently
OL,15,Fimplemented and in which school
OL,16,Fmanagement takes the lead.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
