OL,3,CTeachers on strike over 'abusive pupil
OL,4,Cbehaviour threatening safety' of staff
OL,6,F"Our members have been forced to take
OL,7,Fstrike action in order to secure basic
OL,8,Fworking conditions which should be the
OL,9,Fexpected norm in every school. It
OL,10,Fshould not have had to come to this
OL,11,Fand the responsibility for any
OL,12,Fdisruption caused by the strike action
OL,13,Frests firmly with school management."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@eO]
