OL,4,Cbehaviour threatening safety' of staff
OL,6,FA spokesperson for Tewkesbury Academy
OL,7,Fsaid: "Some staff at Tewkesbury
OL,8,FAcademy have voted to participate in
OL,9,Fstrikes organised by the National
OL,10,FEducation Union and teachers' union
OL,11,FNASUWT. This action primarily relates
OL,12,Fto the management of behaviour of a
OL,13,Fsmall minority of students and the
OL,14,Fimplementation of approaches designed
OL,15,Fto improve standards for all children.
OL,26,@oD@GOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
