OL,3,CTeachers on strike over 'abusive pupil
OL,4,Cbehaviour threatening safety' of staff
OL,6,F"We are surprised and saddened that
OL,7,Funions have opted for action despite
OL,8,Fthe significant progress which has
OL,9,Fbeen made in our talks. Nevertheless,
OL,10,Fwe remain firmly committed to
OL,11,Fnegotiating in good faith to reduce
OL,12,Fdisruption for families and to ensure
OL,13,Fall children in our town can enjoy a
OL,14,Fgood education and success in life."
